    "slug": "charles-says-that-he-does-not-care-what-sort-of-jane-i-am-so-long-as-i-am-his-ja",
    "texto": "Charles says that he does not care what sort of Jane I am so long as I am his Jane; Sardar says that he does not care what sort of Jane I am so long as I am my own Jane; Sahjara says that she does not care what sort of Jane I am so long as she is my Sahjara. Thus I am daily three Janes, and so the luckiest of all.",
